data.description: This stunning Perry one story home is ideally located on a cul de sac street in the community of Lakeshore and is zoned to fantastic Humble ISD schools! This home features an open entryway with tall ceilings, a gorgeous study and formal dining room with wood flooring, an island kitchen with exotic granite counters and stainless steel appliances, large living room with gas fire place, primary retreat with wood floors and an en suite bath with dual vanities, separate shower, soaking tub, and two large walk in closets! There are three ample secondary bedrooms and two additional full bathrooms! The covered back patio overlooks the perfectly sized back yard! There is a mud room bench and a garage that has an extension for extra storage! Refrigerator, washer, and dryer are included! Within close proximity of Lakeshore Elementary! Neighborhood amenities include a fitness center, clubhouse, pool, tennis courts, and parks!
